  "comment": "LMB1040IP Outdoor Moving Bar with Zoom: The LMB1040 is a high-performance weatherproof LED bar that produces a powerful zoomable range of movable light via its ten RGBW 4-in-1 40W high-quality LEDs. Each pixel can be controlled individually, and the light output can be easily converted into dynamic bundles full of numerous beams. This bright, moving pixel bar features a zoom range of 3º to 37º, a linear dimmer from 0 to 100%, an electronic strobe and a variable colour temperature from 2,700 K to 8,000 K. The fixture can be used on the ground or can be quickly and easily hung from a truss with the supplied Omega brackets.\n\n\n",
